368  void JustSummoned(Creature* cr) override
369  {
370  summons.Summon(cr);
371  if (cr->GetEntry() >= NPC_FREYA_KEEPER && cr->GetEntry() <= NPC_THORIM_KEEPER)
372  {
373  if (cr->GetEntry() == NPC_FREYA_KEEPER)
374  cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_CONJURE_SANITY_WELL, false);
375  _keepersGUID[cr->GetEntry() - NPC_FREYA_KEEPER] = cr->GetGUID();
376  }
377  else if (cr->GetEntry() == NPC_SANITY_WELL)
378  cr->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_STATE, SPELL_AURA_MOD_SCALE, true);
379  }

381  void SpawnClouds()
382  {
383  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
384  {
385  float Zplus = i > 2 ? (i - 2) * 1.6f : 0;
386  if (i % 2)
387  me->SummonCreature(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD, me->GetPositionX() + 8 + i * 7, me->GetPositionY() + 8 + i * 7, 326 + Zplus, 0);
388  else
389  me->SummonCreature(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD, me->GetPositionX() - 8 - i * 7, me->GetPositionY() - 8 - i * 7, 326 + Zplus, 0);
390  }
391  }

414  void EnableSara(bool apply)
415  {
416  if (apply)
417  {
418  me->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_DISABLE_MOVE);
419  me->DisableRotate(false);

430  void Reset() override
431  {
432  summons.DoAction(ACTION_DESPAWN_ADDS);
433  events.Reset();
434  summons.DespawnAll();
435 
436  me->SetVisible(true);
437  me->SetDisplayId(me->GetNativeDisplayId());
438  me->SetDisableGravity(true);
439  EnableSara(false);
440  SpawnClouds();
441 
442  _initFight = 1;
443 
444  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
445  _keepersGUID[i].Clear();
446 
447  _summonedGuardiansCount = 0;
448  _p2TalkTimer = 0;
449  _secondPhase = false;
450  _summonSpeed = 1.0f;
451  _currentIllusion = urand(1, 3);
452  _isIllusionReversed = urand(0, 1);
453 
454  if (m_pInstance)
455  {
456  m_pInstance->DoStopTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, CRITERIA_NOT_GETTING_OLDER);
457  m_pInstance->DoRemoveAurasDueToSpellOnPlayers(SPELL_SANITY);
458  m_pInstance->SetData(TYPE_YOGGSARON, NOT_STARTED);
459  if (GameObject* go = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, m_pInstance->GetGuidData(GO_YOGG_SARON_DOORS)))
460  go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
461  }
462  }

464  void InitFight(Unit* target)
465  {
466  if (!m_pInstance)
467  return;
468 
469  // some simple hack checks
470  if (m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_VEZAX) != DONE || m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_XT002) != DONE)
471  return;
472 
473  m_pInstance->DoStartTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, CRITERIA_NOT_GETTING_OLDER);
474  m_pInstance->SetData(TYPE_YOGGSARON, IN_PROGRESS);
475  me->SetInCombatWithZone();
476  AttackStart(target);
477 
478  me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_SANITY_BASE, true);
479 
480  SaveKeepers();
481 
482  events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_DOORS_CLOSE, 15000, 0, EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
483  events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_BERSERK, 900000, 0, 0);
484  events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_SUMMON, 0, 0, EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
485  events.SetPhase(EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
486 
487  me->Yell("The time to strike at the head of the beast will soon be upon us! Focus your anger and hatred on his minions!", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
488  me->PlayDirectSound(SARA_AGGRO);
489  me->setActive(true);
490  }
491 
492  void SaveKeepers()
493  {
494  for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
495  if (m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_WATCHERS) & (1 << i))
496  switch (i)
497  {
498  case KEEPER_FREYA:
499  SpawnWeels();
500  me->SummonCreature(NPC_FREYA_KEEPER, 1939.32f, 42.165f, 338.415f, 5.17955f);
501  break;
502  case KEEPER_HODIR:
503  me->SummonCreature(NPC_HODIR_KEEPER, 1939.13f, -90.8332f, 338.415f, 1.00123f);
504  break;
505  case KEEPER_MIMIRON:
506  me->SummonCreature(NPC_MIMIRON_KEEPER, 2036.81f, 25.6646f, 338.415f, 3.74227f);
507  break;
508  case KEEPER_THORIM:
509  me->SummonCreature(NPC_THORIM_KEEPER, 2036.59f, -73.8499f, 338.415f, 2.34819f);
510  break;
511  }
512  }

514  void InformCloud()
515  {
516  Creature* cloud = nullptr;
517  for (SummonList::const_iterator itr = summons.begin(); itr != summons.end();)
518  {
519  Creature* summon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, *itr);
520  ++itr;
521  if (!summon || summon->GetEntry() != NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD || me->GetDistance(summon) < 20)
522  continue;
523 
524  if ((!cloud || (urand(0, 1) && !summon->HasAura(SPELL_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_OF_YS))))
525  cloud = summon;
526  }
527 
528  if (cloud)
529  cloud->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_START_SUMMONING);
530  }

532  void SpawnTentacle(uint32 entry)
533  {
534  uint32 dist = urand(38, 48);
535  float o = rand_norm() * M_PI * 2;
536  float Zplus = (dist - 38) / 6.5f;
537  if (Creature* cr = me->SummonCreature(entry, me->GetPositionX() + dist * cos(o), me->GetPositionY() + dist * sin(o), 327.2 + Zplus, 0, TEMPSUMMON_CORPSE_TIMED_DESPAWN, 5000))
538  {
539  cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_TENTACLE_ERUPT, true);
540  cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_VOID_ZONE_SMALL, true);
541  cr->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EMERGE);
542  }
543  }

556  void AddPortals()
557  {
558  _summonSpeed -= 0.1f;
559  Creature* cr = nullptr;
560 
561  // Spawn Portals
